    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! It\u2019s actually a bit bittersweet to be posting this, but it\u2019s time for my absolute pride and joy to find a new home. I\u2019ve spent more weekends than I can count polishing this beauty, and honestly, it looks just as stunning as the day I first saw it in the showroom. It\u2019s been tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and still has that 'fresh off the lot' feel that\u2019s so hard to find these days. There might be a tiny, nearly invisible mark if you really go hunting with a magnifying glass, but to my eyes, she\u2019s perfect. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for like a member of the family, you\u2019ve found it. Come on by, let's grab a coffee, and I'll show you why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
      "price": 44500.0,
